# LLDB init for `zig build run_x64 -Ddebug=true`: QEMU exposes a GDB-protocol
# stub on localhost:1234 and starts frozen (-S) until a debugger attaches.
#
# LLDB sources a project-local .lldbinit only if you either launch from this
# directory with `--local-lldbinit`, or add
# `settings set target.load-cwd-lldbinit true` to your own ~/.lldbinit once.
#
# For arm instead of x64, or a test kernel instead of the release one:
#   file zig-out/arm/kernel
#   file zig-out/x64/kernel_test
#   file zig-out/arm/kernel_test

file zig-out/x64/kernel
gdb-remote localhost:1234
